          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The spectrographically pure holmium oxide (Ho2O3)",
                "powder was used to prepare the samples for reactor",
                "neutron irradiation. About 3-5 mg Ho2O3 was weighed",
                "on a Sartorius micro balance under controlled",
                "humidity conditions. The samples of cobalt [using",
                "wires of aluminum-cobalt (0.475%) alloy and pure",
                "cobalt], gold [Al-Au (0.1143%) alloy foil], zirconium",
                "foil and zinc were prepared for flux characterization",
                "of the irradiation position and to determine the",
                "1/E deviation parameter."
              ]
            }
          ],
